item.title: New Photo set on Flickr
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: I've just uploaded a new set of photo's from last weekend. We were down in Hollywood (Florida) for my cousin's engagement party. After the party my parent's and Christine ended up at Ft. Lauderdale beach, so here's some pictures from us hanging out. Check some of them out
